### Create a visit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/visits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "c-1001",
  "customerName": "Acme Clinic",
  "notes": "Intro meeting; follow up in 2 weeks",
  "visitedAt": "2026-06-12T15:00:00Z"
}

### List visits (paged)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/visits?page=0&size=20&sort=visitedAt,desc

### Get one visit (paste an id from the create/list response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/visits/REPLACE_WITH_ID

### Update a visit
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/visits/REPLACE_WITH_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Acme Clinic (HQ)",
  "notes": "Updated after call",
  "visitedAt": "2026-06-12T15:00:00Z"
}

### Delete a visit
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/visits/REPLACE_WITH_ID

### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
